---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="首页" description="Iscream 的个人博客" showSakura={true}>
  <div class="relative z-10 min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-4 pt-24 pb-16">
    <!-- Profile Section -->
    <div class="text-center animate-fade-in max-w-2xl">
      <div class="w-28 h-28 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 overflow-hidden border-3 border-white/80 shadow-lg ring-2 ring-hyouka-sakura/30">
        <img src="https://github.com/ahjy51.png" alt="Iscream" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      </div>

      <h1 class="hyouka-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-2">
        Iscream
      </h1>
      <p class="text-hyouka-ink-light dark:text-gray-400 mb-1">
        古典部 部員
      </p>
      <p class="text-hyouka-mist dark:text-gray-500 text-sm mb-6">
        好奇心駆動型の開発者 / Android & Web
      </p>

      <div class="flex justify-center gap-3 mb-8">
        <a href="https://github.com/ahjy51" target="_blank"
           class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/70 dark:bg-gray-800/70 backdrop-blur-sm 
                  text-sm text-hyouka-ink-light dark:text-gray-300 
                  border border-hyouka-mist/30 dark:border-gray-700/30
                  hover:bg-hyouka-sakura/10 hover:border-hyouka-sakura/30 transition-all">
          GitHub
        </a>
        <a href="/blog"
           class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-hyouka-sakura/80 dark:bg-pink-800/80 backdrop-blur-sm
                  text-sm text-white
                  hover:bg-hyouka-sakura transition-all">
          浏览博客
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="hyouka-card p-6 text-left">
        <p class="text-sm text-hyouka-ink-light dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed italic">
          「日々、私たちが過ごしている日常は、実は奇跡の連続なのかもしれない。」
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-hyouka-mist dark:text-gray-500 mt-2 text-right">
          — 折木奉太郎 『氷菓』
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Latest Posts Preview -->
      <div class="mt-10 text-left">
        <h2 class="hyouka-heading text-lg mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="w-1 h-4 bg-hyouka-sakura rounded-full inline-block"></span>
          最新文章
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <a href="/blog/hello-world" class="block hyouka-card p-4 hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-medium text-hyouka-ink dark:text-gray-100 mb-1">Hello World</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-hyouka-mist dark:text-gray-500">2026-06-28</p>
              </div>
              <span class="hyouka-tag shrink-0">日常</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
